{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"304 Not Modified","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/HTTP/Status/304","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\">El código HTTP&nbsp;de&nbsp;redirección &nbsp;<code><strong>304 Not Modified</strong></code>&nbsp;en el response de la petición indica que no hay necesidad de retransmitir los recursos solicitados. Es una redirección implícita a un elemento/recurso de caché.</div>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\">Esto sucede cuando el método de la solicitud es&nbsp;<a href=\"/es/docs/Glossary/safe\">seguro</a> (<a href=\"/es/docs/Glossary/safe\">safe</a>), como en el las peticiones con métodos&nbsp;<a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTTP/Methods/GET\"><code>GET</code></a> o <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Methods/HEAD\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">HEAD (en-US)</a>, o cuando el request (petición) está condicionada y usa la cabecera&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/If-None-Match\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">If-None-Match (en-US)</a> o un <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/If-Modified-Since\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">If-Modified-Since (en-US)</a></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect4\">El response <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTTP/Status/200\"><code>200</code></a> <code>OK</code>&nbsp;habría incluido los encabezados&nbsp;<a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Cache-Control\"><code>Cache-Control</code></a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Location\"><code>Content-Location</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Date\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Date (en-US)</a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/ETag\"><code>ETag</code></a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Expires\"><code>Expires</code></a>, y <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Vary\"><code>Vary</code></a>.</div>\n\n<div id=\"sect5\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect6\">\n<p>Muchos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://firefox-source-docs.mozilla.org/devtools-user/network_monitor/index.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">developer tools' network panels</a>&nbsp;(paneles&nbsp;de red de desarrollo) de los navegadores crean extraños request que conducen a un \"response(respuesta del servidor)&nbsp;<code>304</code>&nbsp;\", entonces el acceso al caché local es accesible a los desarrollodares.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"status","title":"Status","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">304 Not Modified</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"Especificaciones","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificación</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Título</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc7232#section-4.1\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 7232, section 4.1: 304 Not Modified</a></td>\n   <td>Hypertext Transfer Protocol (HTTP/1.1): Conditional Requests</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad en navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_en_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"http.status.304","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/HTTP/Status/304/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas_de_compatibilidad","title":"Notas de compatibilidad","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Browser behavior differs if this response erroneously includes a body on persistent connections See <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Status/204\">204 No Content</a> for more detail.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/If-Modified-Since\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">If-Modified-Since (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/If-None-Match\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">If-None-Match (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Status","id":"status"},{"text":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad en navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_en_navegadores"},{"text":"Notas de compatibilidad","id":"notas_de_compatibilidad"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"","popularity":0.001,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"304 Not Modified","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"304 Not Modified","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"304 Not Modified","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"304 Not Modified","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"304 Not Modified","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"304 Not Modified","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"304 Not Modified","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"304 Not Modified","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/http/status/304","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/http/status/304/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTTP","title":"HTTP"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTTP/Status","title":"Códigos de estado de respuesta HTTP"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTTP/Status/304","title":"304 Not Modified"}],"pageTitle":"304 Not Modified - HTTP | MDN","noIndexing":false}}